cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision and graphics problems related to shading effects in images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves crowdsourcing and machine learning, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) respectively. The use of convolutional neural networks suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category. Finally, the dataset is generated from RGB-D imagery, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
